<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>{% block title %}Welcome!{% endblock %}</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com"/>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Raleway:wght@100;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@300;400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
    {% block stylesheets %}
        {{ encore_entry_link_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}
    {% block javascripts %}
        <script>
          let toasts = {{ app.session.flashbag.get('toast')|json_encode|raw }};
        </script>
        {{ encore_entry_script_tags('app') }}
    {% endblock %}
</head>
<body class="min-h-dvh bg-slate-950 text-slate-900 antialiased">
<div id="root" class="relative min-h-dvh overflow-hidden">
    <div
            class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-contain bg-center bg-no-repeat opacity-35"
            style="background-image: url('{{ asset('background-blue.jpg') }}'); "
    ></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/45"></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-br from-sky-900/35 via-cyan-900/25 to-indigo-950/45"></div>
    <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(circle_at_10%_20%,rgba(255,255,255,0.18),transparent_35%),radial-gradient(circle_at_80%_0%,rgba(125,211,252,0.25),transparent_25%)]"></div>

    <div class="relative mx-auto grid min-h-screen w-full max-w-7xl gap-8 px-4 py-6 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_30rem] lg:px-8 lg:py-10">
        <aside class="hidden lg:flex lg:flex-col lg:justify-between">
            <div class="max-w-xl space-y-6 text-white">
                <p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.25em] text-sky-200">Plateforme</p>
                <h1 class="text-5xl font-black leading-tight tracking-tight">{{ product_name }}</h1>
                <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold leading-relaxed text-sky-100">
                    Outil de Redaction de l'Offre de Formation
                </h2>
                <p class="max-w-lg text-base text-sky-100/85">
                    Centralisez vos demandes, simplifiez les echanges et connectez-vous rapidement avec votre compte
                    institutionnel.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div class="flex items-center gap-5 text-sky-100/90">
                <a href="mailto:oreof@univ-reims.fr" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                   class="transition hover:text-white" aria-label="Contacter l'equipe ORéOF">
                    <i class="fal fa-envelope text-lg"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://github.com/Dannebicque/oreof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                   class="transition hover:text-white" aria-label="Depôt GitHub ORéOF">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-github text-lg"></i>
                </a>
                <a href="https://twitter.com/davidannebicque" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                   class="transition hover:text-white" aria-label="Profil Twitter">
                    <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter text-lg"></i>
                </a>
            </div>
        </aside>

        <main class="flex items-center">
            <section class="w-full rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-6 shadow-2xl md:p-8">
                <div class="mb-8 flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
                    <img src="{{ asset('images/logo_urca.png') }}" alt="Logo URCA" class="h-14 w-auto" loading="lazy">
                    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-sky-50 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-sky-700">
                        <i class="fa-duotone fa-pencil-ruler"></i>
                        <span>{{ product_name }}</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                {% block content %}{% endblock %}

                <footer class="mt-10 border-t border-slate-200 pt-5 text-sm text-slate-600">
                    <p>&copy; 2023 David Annebicque // Emeline Lang-Lannoy -
                        version {{ user_data.version|default('n/a') }}</p>
                    <div class="mt-3 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-3 gap-y-2">
                        <a href="#"
                           class="font-medium text-slate-700 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-slate-900">Docs</a>
                        <span aria-hidden="true" class="text-slate-300">|</span>
                        <details class="group inline-block">
                            <summary
                                    class="cursor-pointer list-none font-medium text-slate-700 underline decoration-slate-300 underline-offset-4 transition hover:text-slate-900">
                                Usage des donnees
                            </summary>
                            <div class="mt-3 max-w-2xl space-y-2 rounded-xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-4 text-sm text-slate-600">
                                <p>Ce site n'enregistre aucune donnee sur votre utilisation de l'outil.</p>
                                <p>Un seul cookie est utilise pour gerer la connexion lorsque vous activez l'option "se
                                    souvenir de moi" sur la page de connexion.</p>
                                <p>Les fichiers de log sont anonymes et ne contiennent pas d'informations personnelles
                                    vous concernant.</p>
                            </div>
                        </details>
                    </div>
                    <div class="mt-4 flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-400 lg:hidden">
                        <a href="mailto:oreof@univ-reims.fr" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                           class="transition hover:text-slate-700" aria-label="Contacter l'equipe ORéOF">
                            <i class="fal fa-envelope text-lg"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://github.com/Dannebicque/oreof" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                           class="transition hover:text-slate-700" aria-label="Depôt GitHub ORéOF">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-github text-lg"></i>
                        </a>
                        <a href="https://twitter.com/davidannebicque" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"
                           class="transition hover:text-slate-700" aria-label="Profil Twitter">
                            <i class="fa-brands fa-twitter text-lg"></i>
                        </a>
                    </div>
                </footer>
            </section>
        </main>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
